title: Continue 10,000 $JAMM/month salary for Shreyas
body:
I propose that we continue to pay 10,000 $JAMM to Shreyas as Community Manager for JammSession. 

To change Shreyas's salary, we need an equal or higher quorum than the initial proposal: https://snapshot.page/#/jamm/proposal/QmU8xvQefUD5BSn7uqGfvNRC2MadHSqWAenphjyCds5GxD
